{"tid":2044261,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消息：威院初步確診無外遊病人丈夫亦初步確診","createTime":"2020-05-31T04:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T13:14:45.000Z","uid":184261,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8909ffb35c2f5069a6746c7a3bd6e842f3a5c975","tid":2044261,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:09:46.000Z","msg":"Source: 支那01"},{"pid":"92f8a43bffd22c21471b6c3130658b6b770f8815","tid":2044261,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61cb8c6a01a9bfbb487ffc109d512be5e1b02d5","tid":2044261,"uid":184261,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:10:26.000Z","msg":"本港新冠肺炎疫情反覆，昨天新增3宗輸入個案，令累計個案增至1,083宗，同時或增一宗懷疑本地感染個案。消息指，一名34歲女病人昨晚（30日）初步對新冠病毒檢測呈陽性，她昨天被送往沙田威爾斯親王醫院深切治療部留醫，病情危殆，需用呼吸機維生。由於她近期沒有外遊紀錄，如最終確診，或成本地感染個案，令連續16日零本地感染「斷纜」。<br />\n<br />\n這名女病人是否確診將對本港未來防疫政策十分關鍵，料今天下午衞生防護中心將會召開記者會交代事件。"},{"pid":"145666cf463cb4adc1d91e4fbdeafc39088e90d7","tid":2044261,"uid":266342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:10:51.000Z","msg":"永續限聚.令"},{"pid":"2a9cb63815db9c23c180f9fbacbea13c4d3f27ec","tid":2044261,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:10:58.000Z","msg":"0 &gt; 1<br />\n+無限%<br />\n大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e01ece16c027f1dc8d7d2625009d550666cc68b","tid":2044261,"uid":115096,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:24:12.000Z","msg":"兩公婆最近有冇收過淘寶寄來港貨物呀？"},{"pid":"8fcba427702e144fa52fe9529d4e9f7645bcb564","tid":2044261,"uid":179718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:25:58.000Z","msg":"港共：永續限聚令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid